  <p class="content"><p>Medical Acoustics’ mission is to design and develop devices employing acoustic technologies for diagnostic and therapeutic medical applications. It is a privately held, commercial-stage medical device company located in Buffalo, New York, that has been built on ten years of research and development in the science of applied acoustics.</p>
<p>The Company’s first product, the patented Lung Flute®, is a revolutionary medical device which is expected to play a significant role in the treatment, diagnosis of and drug development for lung cancer, tuberculosis, chronic bronchitis, asthma and community-acquired pneumonia. The Lung Flute® has been cleared by the FDA for diagnostic use and is expected to receive clearance for therapeutic use in the U.S. in the near future. It has also received the CE mark clearance for use in the European Union.</p>
<p>Hope it will helpful for yours,thanks.<br />
